address those concerns consistent with the enumerated
reconfiguration standards.
<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">2</NUMEX>) To the extent reasonably practical, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">LSC</ENAMEX>'s state planning team
