<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">4</NUMEX>) If the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">LSC</ENAMEX> state planning <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">team</ENAMEX> recommends a service area
