objections.
<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">7</NUMEX>) Upon such a request, the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">President</ENAMEX> will convene a
face-to-face meeting with the authorized <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">representatives</ENAMEX> of the
